snippet.textDisplay: My God ! This IS a pure trip, with music and CYMATICS, not drugs ! A metal bowl filled with water was put on the diaphragm of a bass speaker put vertically and the sound graphs was being created on the water bowl with the vibration of that bass speaker. The changing pattern in sand graph due to the vibration is there as well in the hind sight ! Sound vibration was also visually depicted by the flames in the Reuben's Tube ! Tell me, the vibration created by the water bowl - was it 432 MHz??? @Arnab, Please tell me man ! That's the vibration through which the music can easily, seamlessly connect to the soul not the usual 440 MHz we listen to, unknowingly. I was feeling the "Anondodhara" inside me ! Man ! this is phenomenal much more than mind blowing !
